{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=2c7efbb5229da21c908a8e45057d2b7b&src=http%3A%2F%2Fa.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Feac4b74543a982269781810b8282b9014a90eb5e.jpg","summary":"怀化学院(Huaihua University)，坐落于古有“滇黔门户、全楚咽喉”之称的怀化市，是一所省属的全日制普通本科院校。学院创办于1958年，前身是怀化师范高等专科学校，2002年经国家教育部批准升格为本科院校。截止2014年9月，学校学校占地1100余亩，建筑面积42万平方米，分东、西两个校区办学，拥有馆藏图书123万册，电子图书232万册，中文期刊1827种；教学科研仪器设备总值达1.06亿元。学校先后被评为“湖南省文明单位”、“湖南省文明高校”、“全国精神文明建设工作先进单位”。","tags":["综合类","本科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1958","所在地区":"湖南省怀化市迎丰东路612号","院校隶属":"湖南省教育厅"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=e666b6602d384f3d82a8caf2b2e4cbde&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3681433312%2C846631050%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=fd48d9db01c08e0d0316990876412821&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3626325267%2C868520217%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=f51e6c425d8c24aa76c30f925dc9fe45&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3636039282%2C3972972269%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=1b37a0b2434b7a896bad0763bf22a480&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3397351030%2C3597451022%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=ef0155eee693dec3b3290b8f88be56b2&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3635255836%2C962244102%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=a81c992365f8d09